// Non-throwing. Uses access(path, F_OK) then stat to differentiate dir/file.
//
// Slot usage:
//   slot 0 = path *
//   slot 1 = cstr ptr
//   slot 2 = access result
//   slot 3 = stat buffer ptr (144 bytes)
//   slot 4 = stat result
